    Fe+++               0.37e-3 M Fe(OH)3
    Fe++                0.37e-10
    NH4+                1.0e-15
    Tracer              1.0e-15
    Tracer1             1.0e-15
    CH4(aq)             1.0e-20
    SO4--               1.d-20
